{"tid":381922,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"大家剪頭髮剪到一半 唔滿意會點做？","createTime":"2017-08-31T10:20:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-03T13:52:14.000Z","uid":25902,"like":52,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"846541751a81e6f7adc5bba65bc3ee69c563de9b","tid":381922,"uid":25902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T10:20:57.000Z","msg":"是咁的 上個月去剪頭髮 留左好耐 <br />\n之後我去左平時間髮型屋到 比張相個髮型師<br />\n同佢講 我想電到咁樣啊 佢話ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n電完剪完 同張相電完既效果相差10萬8千里<br />\n不過電得太多 爆爆地 厚同長都幾好 反而自己幾中意<br />\n<br />\n我未試過咁滿意自己個頭<br />\n番工炒散 d人都話我靚仔左 仲即刻有女鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後直到o岩o岩 劇情就咁轉直下<br />\n<br />\n我照樣搵番個髮型師剪 同佢講 我測邊d雜草生左出黎 想鏟左佢 佢話ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後鏟撚完側邊 佢開始幫我偷薄<br />\n咁我心諗 ok既 反正呢排開始做gym跑步 天氣又熱<br />\n之後條仆街愈偷愈多 我出聲講<br />\n<br />\n會唔會薄得濟？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條撚樣話 唔薄啊 係你o岩先太厚姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仆街 我心諗 屌你老母 我過黎話鏟青炸冇叫你偷薄我啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n偷薄完都算 佢仲開始剪我前面d陰 又係愈剪愈多<br />\n<br />\n我出聲同佢講 會唔會太短？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n條撚樣話 唔會唔會 邊到短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後剪哂 我同佢講 短左d薄左d喎好似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢就話 唔薄啊 點會薄 而家咪似一開始你比張相個個頭囉<br />\n<br />\n我真係好燥 燥撚到極點<br />\n之後佢開始幫我gel頭 幫我gel番高佢<br />\n<br />\n我真係屌出聲 心諗 我原本個頭厚到唔洗gel都成到型 你而家幫我gel番高仲話唔薄？<br />\n<br />\n我行出間鋪頭 望住自己個又短又薄既軍裝頭<br />\n我未試過咁唔滿意自己個頭<br />\n個一刻我即刻想衝去買帽 想衝番屋企洗頭吹頭睇下救唔救得番<br />\n<br />\n不過我知道我做乜都冇用 我喊住咁上車番左屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家如果剪到一半 唔滿意會點做？<br />\n同埋想問下大家 邊到剪頭髮好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我已經永遠black list左呢間鋪頭"},{"pid":"d5ce4feee0e2e46ce03b678dfcce67670dcd77d5","tid":381922,"uid":3095,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T10:24:35.000Z","msg":"圖？"},{"pid":"5d8763143378d156c4cd02aecb99e4d6066324f5","tid":381922,"uid":68084,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T10:24:49.000Z","msg":"Ff<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n毒撚邊敢出聲"},{"pid":"f17cf7e84a75a832d224d296be85041c6e734232","tid":381922,"uid":55628,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T10:30:12.000Z","msg":"佢有冇幫你gel 頭先？<br />\n有啲頭要gel 先好睇㗎啦<br />\nI mean 剪完可能好薄"},{"pid":"ba89a3f7e0c4877a8751babeb43e6786b6d8ca20","tid":381922,"uid":137829,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T10:30:59.000Z","msg":"同佢講 剪柒左就燒曬你啲鳩毛"},{"pid":"bce4a74626d9875c625b49cc28e1cce964397f3b","tid":381922,"uid":25902,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T10:32:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢有冇幫你gel 頭先？<br />\n有啲頭要gel 先好睇㗎啦<br />\nI mean 剪完可能好薄</blockquote><br />\n就係原本唔洗gel都好好<br />\n而家gel完成個柒頭咁"},{"pid":"0b0e3be24992eee7c3f7db6bbf5e75bd32cb5f8b","tid":381922,"uid":76098,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T10:32:56.000Z","msg":"冇戴眼鏡睇唔清楚 唔知剪成點 唯有接受命運"},{"pid":"fc04ac408fd26be3e813dfdf753353eb0d7b802a","tid":381922,"uid":25902,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T10:33:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Ff<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n毒撚邊敢出聲</blockquote><br />\n所以我冇出聲...睇住佢將我既生命同未來前碎"},{"pid":"370928916ddbc44cc19d9665112ec5e20a27f41f","tid":381922,"uid":25902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T10:33:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同佢講 剪柒左就燒曬你啲鳩毛</blockquote><br />\n女人來..."},{"pid":"e88892c786238ba39a73f5cce3a82087abee9cd2","tid":381922,"uid":25902,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T10:33:36.000Z